<plot>X-Tension is an add-on to X: Beyond the Frontier. You have to build up your own empire, factories, fly with many different ships through outer space, meet aliens, foreign cultures and species, trade with them or battle them and solve many other missions. Opposed to X Beyond the Frontier, you don't have to follow a linear plot, instead you can choose your missions that can be accepted at any point in the game.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?662189</url></doc>
